		name: "Glue",
		description: "A 50ml bottle of all-purpose glue. This solvent-based formula dries in an hour and can be used on all manner of surfaces and finishes. Paper to plastic, metal to wood, skin to moving vehicle, whatever you're trying to stick together, a quick dab of this stuff will see the job done.",
